    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        ":::\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "## Normal PDF\n",
        "\n",
        "The PDF for a normal distribution is given by,\n",
        "\n",
        "$$ f(x) = \\frac{1}{\\sigma \\sqrt{2 \\pi}} \\exp\\left(-\\frac{1}{2} \\left(\\frac{x-\\mu}{\\sigma}\\right)^2  \\right) $$\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "::: {.small}"
      ],
      "id": "bbc19cf9"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "def norm_pdf(x, μ, σ):\n",
        "  return (1/(σ * np.sqrt(2*np.pi))) * np.exp(-0.5 * ((x - μ)/σ)**2)"
      ],
      "id": "f1ca2a3b",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        ":::\n",
        "\n",
        ". . .\n",
        "\n",
        "::: {.small}"
      ],
      "id": "472828ea"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "norm_pdf(0, 0, 1)"
      ],
      "id": "dce8ede6",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "norm_pdf(np.inf, 0, 1)"
