      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        ":::\n",
        "\n",
        "## Checking the PDF\n",
        "\n",
        "We can check that we've implemented a valid pdf by integrating from $-\\infty$ to $\\infty$,\n",
        "\n",
        ". . .\n",
        "\n",
        "::: {.small}"
