        "\n",
        "# Example 5 <br/> Special Functions\n",
        "\n",
        "## scipy.special\n",
        "\n",
        "Provides implementations of many special mathematical functions commonly used in statistics, physics, and engineering.\n",
        "\n",
        "::: {.small}\n",
        "| Function | Description |\n",
        "|:---------|:------------|\n",
        "| `gamma`, `gammaln` | Gamma function and its log |\n",
        "| `beta`, `betaln` | Beta function and its log |\n",
        "| `factorial`, `comb`, `perm` | Combinatorial functions |\n",
        "| `erf`, `erfc` | Error function and complement |\n",
        "| `expit`, `logit` | Logistic and inverse logistic |\n",
